    <id>https://www.erran.xyz/2019/10/31/Ubuntu1804Conf/</id>
    <published>2019-10-31T14:24:01.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-11-01T04:42:09.490Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><ul><li>电脑或者笔记本启用BISO中EFI模式<ul><li>Ubuntu18.04.3 安装使用U盘安装系统</li><li><a href="https://mirror.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/ubuntu-releases/18.04.3/ubuntu-18.04.3-desktop-amd64.iso" target="_blank" rel="noopener">阿里云镜像: <strong>ubuntu-18.04.3-desktop-amd64</strong></a></li></ul></li><li><p>安装顺序</p><ul><li><p>Windows 10</p><ul><li><p>这里不讨论，正常PE安装即可，就是需要注意的就是引导启动设置单独的分区，即 <strong>EFI系统分区</strong></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/10/31/rTMzSp5BN7acvj1.png" alt></p></li></ul></li><li><p>Ubuntu18.04.3</p><ul><li>U盘启动选择安装Ubuntu系统，语言选择中文安装</li></ul></li></ul><ul><li>勾选最小化安装(<em>如果需要图形或者无线硬件就勾选上</em>)<ul><li>安装类型选择 <strong>其他选项</strong></li><li>分区情况(100GB方案: <strong>根目录:30000MB</strong>, <strong>家目录:70000MB</strong>, <strong>交换分区:8000MB</strong>)<ul><li><strong>安装启动引导器的设备选择Windows10引导分区</strong>(<em>这个需要切换到EFI模式下才有的选项</em>)<a id="more"></a></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p>更换源</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-proposed main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-backports main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-proposed main restricted universe multiverse</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>设置管理员密码及配置管理员账户登录</p><ul><li><p>注释掉两处第三行(<strong>代码块已经处理</strong>)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ head -n 3 /etc/pam.d/gdm-autologin</span><br><span class="line">#%PAM-1.0</span><br><span class="line">auth    requisite       pam_nologin.so</span><br><span class="line"># auth  required    pam_succeed_if.so user != root quiet_success</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ head -n 3 /etc/pam.d/gdm-password</span><br><span class="line">#%PAM-1.0</span><br><span class="line">auth    requisite       pam_nologin.so</span><br><span class="line"># auth  required    pam_succeed_if.so user != root quiet_success</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改最后一行(<strong>代码块已经处理</strong>)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo tail -n 1 /root/.profile</span><br><span class="line">tty -s &amp;&amp; mesg n || true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>允许管理员账户登录(<strong>代码块已经处理</strong>)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ cat /usr/share/lightdm/lightdm.conf.d/50-ubuntu.conf</span><br><span class="line">[Seat:*]</span><br><span class="line">user-session=ubuntu</span><br><span class="line"># greeter-show-manual-login=true</span><br><span class="line"># all-guest=false</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[SeatDefaults]</span><br><span class="line">greeter-session=unity-greeter</span><br><span class="line">allow-guest=false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>管理员账户使用音频(<strong>代码块已经处理</strong>)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ tail -n 1 /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line">pulseaudio --start --log-target=syslog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>使用 <em>sudo</em> 命令不需要输入密码(修改26行，<strong>代码块已经处理</strong>)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo sed -n &apos;26p&apos; /etc/sudoers</span><br><span class="line">%sudo   ALL=(ALL:ALL) NOPASSWD:ALL</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>命令行终端显示段路径(修改62行，<strong>代码块已经处理</strong>)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:share$ sed -n &apos;62p&apos; ~/.bashrc</span><br><span class="line">    PS1=&apos;$&#123;debian_chroot:+($debian_chroot)&#125;\u@\h:\W\$ &apos;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>更新系统应用到最新状态</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo apt autoremove &amp;&amp; sudo apt autoclean &amp;&amp; sudo apt update &amp;&amp; sudo apt upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>解决笔记本插耳机出现异常声音</p><ul><li><p>添加文件 <strong>modprobe.conf</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ cat /etc/modprobe.d/modprobe.conf</span><br><span class="line">options snd-hda-intel model=,generic</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>使用第一条命令进入控制界面后按 <strong>F6</strong> ，选择( <strong>HDA INTEL PCH</strong> )，右移到 <strong>auto mute</strong> 按上方向键关闭，然后按 <strong>Esc</strong> 键退出，最后使用下面第二条命令保存即可</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo alsamixer</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo alsactl store</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>跳过windows 10GRUB引导及显示代码界面(<strong>代码块已经处理</strong>)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo sed -n &quot;6,20p&quot; /etc/default/grub</span><br><span class="line"># GRUB_DEFAULT=0</span><br><span class="line"># GRUB_TIMEOUT_STYLE=hidden</span><br><span class="line"># GRUB_TIMEOUT=10</span><br><span class="line"># GRUB_DISTRIBUTOR=`lsb_release -i -s 2&gt; /dev/null || echo Debian`</span><br><span class="line"># GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT=&quot;quiet splash&quot;</span><br><span class="line"># GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX=&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">GRUB_DEFAULT=0</span><br><span class="line">GRUB_TIMEOUT=0</span><br><span class="line">GRUB_TIMEOUT_STYLE=hidden</span><br><span class="line">GRUB_HIDDEN_TIMEOUT=0</span><br><span class="line">GRUB_HIDDEN_TIMEOUT_QUIET=true</span><br><span class="line">GRUB_DISTRIBUTOR=`lsb_release -i -s 2&gt; /dev/null || echo Debian`</span><br><span class="line">GRUB_DISABLE_OS_PROBER=true</span><br><span class="line">GRUB_RECORDFAIL_TIMEOUT=0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装 <strong>aptitude</strong> 服务，处理依赖问题: <code>evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo apt install aptitude -y</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">aptitude update 更新可用的包列表</span><br><span class="line">aptitude upgrade 升级可用的包</span><br><span class="line">aptitude dist-upgrade 将系统升级到新的发行版</span><br><span class="line">aptitude install pkgname 安装包</span><br><span class="line">aptitude remove pkgname 删除包</span><br><span class="line">aptitude purge pkgname 删除包及其配置文件</span><br><span class="line">aptitude search string 搜索包</span><br><span class="line">aptitude show pkgname 显示包的详细信息</span><br><span class="line">aptitude clean 删除下载的包文件</span><br><span class="line">aptitude autoclean 仅删除过期的包文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>aptitude 解决得更好的地方： install, remove, reinstall（apt-get无此功能）, show（apt-get无此功能）, search（apt-get无此功能）, hold（apt-get无此功能）, unhold（apt-get无此功能）</li><li>apt-get 解决得更好的地方： source（aptitude无此功能）, build-dep （低版本的aptitude没有build-dep功能）</li><li>apt-get 跟 aptitude 没什么区别的地方：update, upgrade (apt-get upgrade=aptitude safe-upgrade, apt-get dist-upgrade=aptitude full-upgrgade)</li></ul></li><li><p>安装 <strong>ntpdate</strong> 服务，处理BIOS时间问题</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo apt install ntpdate -y</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo ntpdate ntp.aliyun.com</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo hwclock --localtime --systohc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装 <strong>iptables-persistent</strong> 服务，处理防火墙无法保存问题</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo apt-get install iptables-persistent -y</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo iptables -nL</span><br><span class="line">Chain INPUT (policy ACCEPT)</span><br><span class="line">target     prot opt source               destination</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Chain FORWARD (policy ACCEPT)</span><br><span class="line">target     prot opt source               destination</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Chain OUTPUT (policy ACCEPT)</span><br><span class="line">target     prot opt source               destination</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 22 -j ACCEPT</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 80 -j ACCEPT</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo netfilter-persistent save</span><br><span class="line">run-parts: executing /usr/share/netfilter-persistent/plugins.d/15-ip4tables save</span><br><span class="line">run-parts: executing /usr/share/netfilter-persistent/plugins.d/25-ip6tables save</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo netfilter-persistent reload</span><br><span class="line">run-parts: executing /usr/share/netfilter-persistent/plugins.d/15-ip4tables start</span><br><span class="line">run-parts: executing /usr/share/netfilter-persistent/plugins.d/25-ip6tables start</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo cat /etc/iptables/rules.v4</span><br><span class="line"># Generated by iptables-save v1.6.1 on Fri Nov  1 11:46:34 2019</span><br><span class="line">*filter</span><br><span class="line">:INPUT ACCEPT [49:2690]</span><br><span class="line">:FORWARD ACCEPT [0:0]</span><br><span class="line">:OUTPUT ACCEPT [76:4521]</span><br><span class="line">-A INPUT -p tcp -m tcp --dport 22 -j ACCEPT</span><br><span class="line">-A INPUT -p tcp -m tcp --dport 80 -j ACCEPT</span><br><span class="line">COMMIT</span><br><span class="line"># Completed on Fri Nov  1 11:46:34 2019</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装搜狗输入法</p><ul><li>安装 <strong>Fcitx</strong> 中文输入法: <code>evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo apt install fcitx -y</code></li><li>安装 <strong>gdebi</strong> 安装包管理: <code>evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo apt install gdebi -y</code></li><li>打开网站下载<a href="https://pinyin.sogou.com/linux/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">搜狗输入法 For Linux</a>最新版本</li><li>安装搜狗输入法: <code>evan@evan-Lenovo:Downloads$ sudo gdebi sogoupinyin_2.3.1.0112_amd64.deb</code></li></ul></li><li><p>安装Python3-pip</p><ul><li>安装pip3: <code>evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo apt install python3-pip -y</code></li><li><p>设置管理员账户镜像源:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo su</span><br><span class="line">root@evan-Lenovo:/home/evan# cat ~/.pip/pip.conf</span><br><span class="line">[global]</span><br><span class="line">timeout = 3000</span><br><span class="line">index-url = https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[install]</span><br><span class="line">timeout = 3000</span><br><span class="line">trusted-host = mirrors.ailiyun.com</span><br><span class="line">root@evan-Lenovo:/home/evan# exit</span><br><span class="line">exit</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>添加当前用户PATH路径</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ tail -n 1 ~/.bashrc</span><br><span class="line">export PATH=/home/evan/.local/bin:$PATH</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>更新pip版本安装及安装requests模块</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo -H python3 -m pip install --upgrade pip</span><br><span class="line">Looking in indexes: https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/</span><br><span class="line">Requirement already up-to-date: pip in /usr/local/lib/python3.6/dist-packages (19.3.1)</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo -H pip3 install requests</span><br><span class="line">Looking in indexes: https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/</span><br><span class="line">Requirement already satisfied: requests in /usr/lib/python3/dist-packages (2.18.4)</span><br><span class="line">evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo su</span><br><span class="line">root@evan-Lenovo:/home/evan# pip3 list | grep requests</span><br><span class="line">requests              2.18.4</span><br><span class="line">requests-unixsocket   0.1.5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>安装优化服务: <code>evan@evan-Lenovo:~$ sudo apt install gnome-tweak-tool chrome-gnome-shell -y</code></p><ul><li>浏览器安装扩展: <a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">gnome shell integration</a></li><li>gnome安装插件: <a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1031/topicons/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TopIcons Plu</a></li><li>gnome安装插件: <a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1160/dash-to-panel/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dash to Panel</a></li><li>gnome安装插件: <a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/19/user-themes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">User Themes</a></li></ul></li><li><p>安装deepin-wine 2.18-19服务(脚本 <strong>阿里云</strong> )</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line">mkdir /tmp/deepintemp</span><br><span class="line">cd /tmp/deepintemp</span><br><span class="line">wget http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/deepin-wine/deepin-wine_2.18-19_all.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/deepin-wine/deepin-wine32_2.18-19_i386.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/deepin-wine/deepin-wine32-preloader_2.18-19_i386.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/deepin-wine-helper/deepin-wine-helper_1.2deepin8_i386.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/deepin-wine-plugin/deepin-wine-plugin_1.0deepin2_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/deepin-wine-plugin-virtual/deepin-wine-plugin-virtual_1.0deepin3_all.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/deepin-wine-uninstaller/deepin-wine-uninstaller_0.1deepin2_i386.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/u/udis86/udis86_1.72-2_i386.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/deepin-wine/deepin-fonts-wine_2.18-19_all.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget http://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/non-free/d/deepin-wine/deepin-libwine_2.18-19_i386.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget https://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/main/libj/libjpeg-turbo/libjpeg62-turbo_1.5.1-2_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget https://mirrors.aliyun.com/deepin/pool/main/libj/libjpeg-turbo/libjpeg62-turbo_1.5.1-2_i386.deb</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">echo &apos;准备添加32位支持&apos;</span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg --add-architecture i386</span><br><span class="line">echo &apos;添加成功，准备刷新apt缓存信息...&apos;</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line">echo &apos;即将开始安装...&apos;</span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg -i &gt;.deb</span><br><span class="line">echo &apos;安装完成，正在自动安装依赖...&apos;</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install -y</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">rm -vfr /tmp/deepintemp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>安装QQ、微信<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span